{"tid":24794,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］點解死唔可以解決問題","createTime":"2016-12-05T17:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T10:36:54.000Z","uid":34132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"850c2647dfd08c40bcbd3127cafffecb5d48ae0d","tid":24794,"uid":34132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"假設個問題係出自自己本身<br />\n死左個問題咪解決左？<br />\n<br />\n頭盔 唔係想教唆他人自殺"},{"pid":"31c1608aa9ec944558c32eb3f5f0c3beff9e5383","tid":24794,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"你死左姐，但問題仲在到"},{"pid":"e175874a9f27a8927c069760cdd99901f26fe908","tid":24794,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"咁要睇咩事啦"},{"pid":"8bda0cd45756cf74adb79acec0bb73ab3c6963e4","tid":24794,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"因為死真係無解決過個問題<br />\n所以死真係解決唔到問題<br />\n<br />\n但或者能夠得到解脫"},{"pid":"704ad2c75a4bd6e19edc8260ebde0356611e4aef","tid":24794,"uid":13127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"死可以解決所有問題<br />\n一齊死"},{"pid":"51de635d8a58b54ada41043ace609b25f3204001","tid":24794,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"解決左你自己問題<br />\n但遺留下更多問題"},{"pid":"bf99177886e0720f24620075066e8b40055edf90","tid":24794,"uid":13127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決左你自己問題<br />\n但遺留下更多問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如呢"},{"pid":"ccee4e2d70dcb705be831cafb940750eacd6ec1a","tid":24794,"uid":4274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"如果死後嘅情況更差 咁你仲死唔死？"},{"pid":"7f3e2236314311af4d502a4195375bb4c4b23c17","tid":24794,"uid":56210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"純粹宗教角度，輪回下世會更慘"},{"pid":"bd9daa4ea0fa2943b50b5c11f5f573a2b3caa81f","tid":24794,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"自殺死後可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學啲，消失<br />\n哲學啲，意識去左虛無<br />\n聖經啲，壞人落地獄，包括自殺<br />\n佛教啲，輪迴做好必既動物<br />\n<br />\n咁當然生存最好"},{"pid":"7cb703f0f13b9c3e6886e7575bf1f6357d3a0603","tid":24794,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自殺死後可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學啲，消失<br />\n哲學啲，意識去左虛無<br />\n聖經啲，壞人落地獄，包括自殺<br />\n佛教啲，輪迴做好必既動物<br />\n<br />\n咁當然生存最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好慘*"},{"pid":"370e5da2454d61c93238f5c854dd9743ddf7a404","tid":24794,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"問題可能你死左轉到你身邊既人. 例如錢.<br />\n你為果個原因而瓜既人會一世比你影響."},{"pid":"a0e3d877115aca25973bcef752a33f22f21b3e10","tid":24794,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊個同你講死解決唔到問題？<br />\n死不嬲解決唔到問題<br />\n但會將你既問題轉移左落人地到<br />\n人地唔想解決你既問題咪叫你唔好自殺囉</span>"},{"pid":"00e56c5ebcac4bc0c176fecc513e3cbd3527c2c8","tid":24794,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>解決左你自己問題<br />\n但遺留下更多問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如呢</blockquote><br />\n如果你係想尋死個答案唔會啱你聽<br />\n有煩惱唔想比身邊人知咪試下係網上講出黎呻下"},{"pid":"9e33e9d53d6f640152774956d560d35e654dac0c","tid":24794,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:04:30.000Z","msg":"你死左冇哂問題，因為問題去左身邊人果道<br />\n所以佢地梗係叫你唔好死，唔好比麻煩佢"},{"pid":"f327b801b5f1d9ee103f8752e75481476a5ee9fc","tid":24794,"uid":56210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊個同你講死解決唔到問題？<br />\n死不嬲解決唔到問題<br />\n但會將你既問題轉移左落人地到<br />\n人地唔想解決你既問題咪叫你唔好自殺囉</span></blockquote><br />\n根據香港法例第33B條《侵害人身罪條例》，任何人協助、教唆、慫使或促致他人自殺，或進行企圖自殺，均屬犯法，最高可判監14年"},{"pid":"962981857c89b6e75e5dd1fe9061af3524351ddd","tid":24794,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"無具體問題好難傾"},{"pid":"4c18a7b80e663679fb1afd49e1cb8e4c1972a543","tid":24794,"uid":7124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊個同你講死解決唔到問題？<br />\n<br />\n死不嬲解決唔到問題<br />\n<br />\n但會將你既問題轉移左落人地到<br />\n<br />\n人地唔想解決你既問題咪叫你唔好自殺囉</span></blockquote><br />\n聽落幾有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ecca2b8e0c38e22c739920e90695da35ccb029","tid":24794,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"自殺都係想報復所有人拋啲問題俾佢地處理，再逼死佢地"}]}